metadata.name: Toby the Tokenaire Cat
metadata.description:
Toby is a dare devil cat with a mysterious pirate past. He loves worms, storms, exploring, chasing exotic birds and swashbuckling.

Toby is a history of chasing the rose ringed parakeets of Telegraph Hill in San Francisco. No one knows how many Toby has caught but he seems to enjoy taking a very bumpy and roundabout way to the destination.
